Definition: resembling or characteristic of a phantom
Example: a ghostly face at the window; a phantasmal presence in the room; spectral emanations; spiritual tappings at a seance
Synonyms: ghostlike, ghostly, noun, person, ghost, attribute, ghostliness, phantasmal, phantasma, cognition, spectral, spiritual, spirit, resembling, or, characteristic, of, a, phantom, face, at, the, window, presence, in, room, emanations, tappings, seance
Category: adj.all
